cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "uniprot-mcp: A Model Context Protocol server for the UniProt protein knowledgebase"
abstract: >-
  uniprot-mcp is a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server exposing ten
  tools that query the UniProt REST API from LLM-driven agents such as
  Claude. It wraps entry retrieval, sequence download, feature and
  variant inspection, GO annotation, cross-reference lookup, ID mapping,
  batch retrieval, and taxonomy search, with strict accession validation,
  retry and back-off, and snapshot-tested formatters.
